Localization.Name: Taos Balaclava and Goggles Ash
Localization.Description: Fearlessly face any weather with the Taos balaclava and goggles. An ultra-soft inner lining provides warmth and comfort while a special exterior coating repels precipitation. The adjustable headband ensures an ideal fit, and the padding of the anti-fog goggles is integrated directly into the fabric to seal out the elements.
